data.description: Plenty of trees. Easy acess to Hwy. 19. Two sets of security gates with openers installed summer 2023.  Deer and hog stand. Crown molding and valted  ceilings in office, dining and master bedroom.  Varmit protected all steel fence in front of property. 20x 26 metal building 11-2020. Covered porches with three ceiling fans on back porch. High speed Fios Internet. Brinks security. 5x7 Safe room and storm shelter. New HVAC 2017 inspected Oct. 2023. New: paint, kitchen & bath facets, vinyl plank floors, stainless steel applicances & tile in the bathrooms. New roof Sept.2023. Walk in lighted pantry. Large living room with scenic view. Large utility room with laundry room with ceiling fan. New wifi opener on the garage. Office. Formal Dining and breakfast nook. Large walk in master closet. Large living room. Room upstairs to put vistors or family. Place to make a garden. Chicken house. Great for a horse or cows. Room to safely play and enjoy the country. Friendly country community.
